\p{I got up early to attend the BCP service at [St. John's](https://www.stjohnscanberra.org/), but was disappointed to see that the service was following the APBA and not the BCP. I think the BCP is only used after January. Furthermore, even by APBA standards the Eucharistic prayer was rushed and insufficiently reverent. Oh well, it is a lovely little church:}
